{"tid":2423872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遲D會唔會有廢老打完科興疫苗之後重新獲得性高潮?","createTime":"2021-02-26T07:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:01:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7b5f4591228dfd2e180fd8147affc2db38f5a1","tid":2423872,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"疫苗接種計劃今日展開，已預約的5個優先群組可在5間疫苗接種中心，及18間醫管局普通科門診接種國產科興疫苗。在銅鑼灣中央圖書館的接種中心，未到早上 8 時開放時間，已有約 20 人在外排隊等候。其中一名市民盧太在接稱疫苗後表示心情「開心、舒服」，指自己「hundred precent」滿意，「自己親自試過後，知道係真嘅、值得打...我就唔再驚個病毒」，又舉起大拇指稱，「等咗好耐，卒之等到國家疫苗到咗... 我哋其實期待好耐，卒之今日有好消息。」<br />\n<br />\n她稱，如果對國產疫苗有疑慮，可選擇等候 另一款BioNTech疫苗，但自己會科興疫苗推介予親友，「中國人嘅疫苗更適合中國人用」、「完全話俾你知冇問題！」<br />\n<br />\n市民區先生亦稱，打針沒有不適，打完反而覺得心情輕鬆，「針窿細到，同我貼膠布都搵唔返個口」，笑言「而家唔打，過幾年要瞓床冇得打啦」。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，接種過程順暢，有專人事前解說，「幾個圍我一個講小冊子」，完成接種後亦有人指示到專區休息，並獲發接種記錄。另外，基本法委員會前副主任、前律政司長梁愛詩 9 時亦來到中央圖書館，準備接種疫苗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/152851957_10165462896035019_1825888625591272653_o_fLPHy_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F152851957_10165462896035019_1825888625591272653_o_fLPHy_1200x0.jpg&h=bef7a9e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69e3921cdf6d38b08dcd6cc6f70d4af092e804b7","tid":2423872,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"係咪打咗同深水埗嗰班自行接種疫苗打嘅一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60cc746d8f3b6c3ff937c997c8361a30c6544f1","tid":2423872,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"噴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c2eee5695722f02dc95d0f31a6d27fb93b0810","tid":2423872,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dhgPLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dhgPLL.jpg&h=051c9966&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n個感覺勁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995719ccdc91bc34582a0bff1b107c51032cb202","tid":2423872,"uid":353587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8yWPPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8yWPPx.png&h=6e8a66f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個阿伯似打咗興奮劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25b9229149dc58bd6db62af6da44858b790ef25","tid":2423872,"uid":267880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"995719ccdc91bc34582a0bff1b107c51032cb202","tid":2423872,"uid":353587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8yWPPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8yWPPx.png&h=6e8a66f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個阿伯似打咗興奮劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"下邊個個咁能大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}